HEADWORD: Emiction
<hw>E*mic"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>e</ets>
out + <ets>mingere</ets>, <ets>mictum</ets>, to make water.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The voiding of urine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>What is voided by the urinary passages;
urine.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Emictory</ent>⟦br⟧
